    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Tootum》 是一款充满魅力的像素风格类银河恶魔城游戏，带领玩家进入一个神秘而充满魔法的世界。在这里，你将体验以魔法为核心的战斗系统、种类丰富的道具以及引人入胜的叙事，踏上一段充满探索与发现的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/385f0bc25bdd7f39e78d83eaceeafd71.poster.avif?t=1755596173\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/385f0bc25bdd7f39e78d83eaceeafd71.webm?t=1755596173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/385f0bc25bdd7f39e78d83eaceeafd71.mp4?t=1755596173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一名来自神秘“魔法协会”的无名使者，被派往被神秘生物侵袭的大陆——冯拉（Vonlar）。你的任务是调查正在发生的一切——但这个世界最深处的秘密，只会向那些勇敢深入隐藏之路的探索者揭示。游戏的故事通过探索过程自然展开，为玩家营造出强烈的沉浸感和好奇心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/bc2e5a0085a6772029fe00055cd0d174.poster.avif?t=1755596173\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/bc2e5a0085a6772029fe00055cd0d174.webm?t=1755596173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/bc2e5a0085a6772029fe00055cd0d174.mp4?t=1755596173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 核心特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔法与策略战斗：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过施放魔法击败怪物，并可根据你选择的魔法书来自定义技能。共有三本魔法书，每本都具有独特属性，将直接影响你的战斗方式和游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直觉式探索：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着冒险的深入，你会发现隐藏的道具，解锁如“墙跳”“灵活移动”等新技能，让探索过程更加流畅有趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个性化成长系统：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过冒险中获得的金币，你可以购买魔法书。你选择的魔法书将决定你的整个战斗与成长路线，打造独一无二的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/4eec1ad24ff5225ad55ba6264e612119.poster.avif?t=1755596173\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/4eec1ad24ff5225ad55ba6264e612119.webm?t=1755596173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3210910/extras/4eec1ad24ff5225ad55ba6264e612119.mp4?t=1755596173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >热情驱动的独立开发作品：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Tootum》由一位独立开发者倾注心血制作，游戏中的氛围、机制以及细节打磨都体现了满满的匠心与热情。</p>",
